                        </div>
                        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3 leading-relaxed">Absolutely gorgeous piece! The fabric quality is exceptional and the fit is perfect. I've received so many compliments wearing this. The attention to detail is remarkable - you can really tell this is a premium piece.</p>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500">
